content: But that number hides some of the advancements that we've made like growth in G2K customers, improved DAP ARR and the growth of greater than $1 million in ARR customers. We've made solid progress expanding our footprint within our G2K customers, but we've also worked hard to drive increased renewals and expansions within these larger customers as evidenced by our dollar-based net retention for customers with over 500 employees staying above 120% in the third quarter. As you may remember, we're happy to already count a number of international governments as our customers, which include one of our largest expansions this quarter, which became our first government entity having over $1 million in ARR.
